# Dependencies — always regenerated by npm ci inside the container
**/node_modules

# Compiled output — always rebuilt inside the container
**/dist

# Secrets — never bake credentials into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Frontend is a separate app and not needed for the backend image
frontend/

# Test artifacts
**/coverage
**/*.test.ts

# Dev tooling
**/bruno
**/.git
**/*.md
